  "caption": "Atelier-style fantasy opening, cheerful and whimsical Celtic folk. Playful pizzicato strings, rhythmic acoustic guitar, and bright glockenspiel accents. Solo tin whistle and elegant violin melody. Light percussion like tambourine and woodblocks. Warm, cozy, and industrious atmosphere. Mid-tempo, 4/4 or 6/8 time, crystalline sound quality.",
